{"tid":511354,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"把握最後機會！Windows 10 免費升級年底結束","createTime":"2017-12-27T11:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T05:23:53.000Z","uid":151933,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"8a46dfab95338ee816b8ddb3668c28b55532b09f","tid":511354,"uid":151933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T11:45:58.000Z","msg":"如果你手上的電腦仍然使用 Windows 7 或 Windows 8 或 8.1 系統，因為各種原因遲遲未有升級至 Windows 10，未來幾天將會升級是最後的機會。原本免費升級 Windows 10 的限期已過，但 Microsoft 為了方便需要使用「輔助技術」的傷殘人士，將限期一再推遲。<br />\n<br />\n用戶只需要登入 Microsoft 專為輔助技術用家而設的 Windows 10 免費升級專頁，下載官方提供的小工具，就可以簡單將舊系統升級。這個內含輔助技術的 Windows 10 系統，普通用戶一樣用得到，換句話說即是免費升級的期間獲得延長。不過 Microsoft 準備將這最後的升級途徑關閉，在官網相關頁面寫著升級的最後限期為 2017 年 12 月 31 日。<br />\n<br />\nMicrosoft 回應傳媒查詢時表示，任何擁有有效產品鑰匙的用戶，均可以在 Media Creation Tool 升級 Windows 10 系統。<br />\n<br />\n來源：wccftech<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/12/27/final-chance-for-windows-10-upgrade/software/win10/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F12%2F27%2Ffinal-chance-for-windows-10-upgrade%2Fsoftware%2Fwin10%2F&d=68iVoqjodNF3NsX5NqndSP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=fbaa4bce\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/12/27/final-chance-for-windows-10-upgrade/software/win10/</a><br />\n<br />\n升左係咪要重新裝番哂d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc52aa652fbcba842b5c97fb87948b9049d8576","tid":511354,"uid":17234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T11:57:02.000Z","msg":"唔洗裝返哂"},{"pid":"6e28f371a58205ebbb9ea92ed3b24e57722d962d","tid":511354,"uid":17234,"like":15,"dislike":7,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T11:57:23.000Z","msg":"覺得win10好用啲"},{"pid":"2e7c51e198d57411175dd3b7100c82c6503fef21","tid":511354,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T12:05:06.000Z","msg":"諗緊升唔升好<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6513d44ab215acc9223c378dbcf6be2f1e731e","tid":5